      <h1 class="text-[2.5rem] md:text-[3.25rem] font-bold mb-6 leading-[1.12]">How Much Does a Postpartum Doula Cost?</h1>
      <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-tjb-gray leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
        <strong>Postpartum doulas</strong> are the support most families don't know they need until they're drowning in dirty diapers and sleep deprivation. Here's what postpartum doula support really costs, what you get for the price, and how to make it work with your budget.
      </p>
